Cozad pitcher Alison Arndt looks to her catcher prior to a pitch against Twin River in the first round of the Class C Softball State Championship on Wednesday in Hastings. Cozad won 11-3 in six innings. (Derek Noehren   Wednesday, October 14, 2015 6:48 pm Cozad advances at state with big win By DEREK NOEHREN dnoehren@nptelegraph.com nptelegraph.com 
HASTINGS — If this group of Cozad softball players had any nerves after making their first state softball appearance — and the program’s first since 2010 — it didn’t show.
